OOC:Oh ok, I just got lost sorta.  Ok, so we went to Zone 5 to recieve
orders, and now Orchestra magically appeared with Darkfate around Hell
Beast's base, and we are under attack....Got it!

IC: Orchestra looked at the base.  He decided to open fire on it!  So he
pulled out his strange gun which shot blue plasma beams.  He fired it at the
base, to see if it still worked as well as it did in the "olden days".

OOC2:  Can I have a list of all of Hell BEast;s members who are currently
out in battle right now so I know who exactly to fire on?
